data.description: This is the one you've been looking for! The Reynolds is proof that great things come in small packages. This smartly-designed ranch makes maximum use of every square foot, with no wasted space. That's how it delivers three spacious bedrooms, two full baths, a true laundry room, and an open kitchen-dining-living area. Bedroom three has the option of being converted into a study for those who need space to work from home, or who just prefer a second living area. This home will feature tray ceilings, granite kitchen countertops and luxurious laminate plank flooring. Don't let it slip away! Ask the listing agent about $4,000 for closing costs by using a Preferred Lender.
